Aqui o <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1JH_xJOjeN1Btt2Ht0IWTD3kG_tXvF62xrKYU5UKWvso/edit#slide=id.g3f3cb59c2_0215">link da palestra</a>.</p>

